import React from 'react';
import RepositoryItem from '../repository-item';
import * as S from './styled';

const Repositories = () => {
  return (
   <S.WrapperTabs
    selectedTabClassName="is-selected"
    selectedTabPanelClassName="is-selected"
   >
     <S.WrapperTabList>
       <S.WrapperTab>Repositories</S.WrapperTab>
       <S.WrapperTab>Starred</S.WrapperTab>
     </S.WrapperTabList>
    <S.WrapperTabPanel>
      <RepositoryItem 
      name="basecamp-javascript" 
      linkToRepo="https://github.com/alessoares/basecamp-javascript" 
      fullName = "alessoares/basecamp-javascript"
      />
    </S.WrapperTabPanel>
    <S.WrapperTabPanel>
      <RepositoryItem
      name="contador" 
      linkToRepo="https://github.com/alessoares/contador" 
      fullName = "alessoares/contador"
      />
    </S.WrapperTabPanel>
   </S.WrapperTabs>
  )
};

export default Repositories;
